    Class Description
    Enemy
    abstract class for the 3 possible enemies.
    Enemy1
    enemy 1 is an extension of the Enemy super class.
    Enemy2
    enemy 2 is an extension of the enemy super class.
    Enemy3
    enemy 3 is an extension of the enemy super class.
    Game

    GameMap

    LocatedImage
    used to keep and get access to image URL
    Map_Easy
    an extension of GameMap.
    Map_Hard
    an extension of GameMap.
    Map_Intermediate
    an extension of GameMap.
    Player
    models one player that is playing on a GameMap.
    SaverLoader
    handles all of the loading and saving functions
    Tile
    models a single Tile on the GameMap being used.
    Tile_Destroy
    an extension of TileContent.
    Tile_Empty

    Tile_Path
    an extenstion of TileContent.
    Tile_Spawn
    an extension of TileContent.
    TileContent
    every Tile contains a TileContent object.
    Tower
    Models a tower to be places onto a GameMap and that will attack the enemies.
    TowerA
    an extension of Tower.
    TowerB
    an extension of Tower.
    TowerC
    an extension of Tower.
  • Enum Summary

    TileType

    TowerType

  • Exception Summary
